rows.label: bf10240170_0010
rows.name: After processing all that information,n\I became certain.

rows.label: bf10240170_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf10240170_0030
rows.name: You all

rows.label: bf10240170_0040
rows.name: have not changed a single thing from how we once were.

rows.label: bf10240170_0050
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]--!!

rows.label: bf10240170_0060
rows.name: So I chose to do nothing about it...

rows.label: bf10240170_0070
rows.name:
500 years ago, when that man finally
reached this place

rows.label: bf10240170_0080
rows.name: I did nothing when he took Logos and Pneuma away

rows.label: bf10240170_0090
rows.name:
The fact that Logos, who materialized as a Blade,
tried to annihilate the world...

rows.label: bf10240170_0100
rows.name: That's strange. Didn't you want to regenerate the world?

rows.label: bf10240170_0110
rows.name: Then why...

rows.label: bf10240170_0120
rows.name: Fate.

rows.label: bf10240170_0130
rows.name: Fate?

rows.label: bf10240170_0140
rows.name:
It was destined to happen.
It could not have happened any other way.

rows.label: bf10240170_0150
rows.name: My sins can never be atoned for.

rows.label: bf10240170_0160
rows.name: That can't be-

rows.label: bf10240170_0170
rows.name:
I had accepted this fate.
Once again, I simply wished to disappear.

rows.label: bf10240170_0180
rows.name: However...

rows.label: bf10240170_0190
rows.name: Something changed.

rows.label: bf10240170_0200
rows.name: And that is you, Rex, along with Pneuma.

rows.label: bf10240170_0210
rows.name: Me and...Homura and Hikari...?

rows.label: bf10240170_0220
rows.name:
You achieved a bond that should
have been impossible, and a shared existence.
